Hello everyone ! I created this topic so I don't have to spam the forums like some others always did :p 
Here am showing my newest videos about my newest redstone creations ! 

Newest video:

A Scientifc Calculator in Minecraft capable of doing Logarithms, Expoential functions and trigonometry!
